### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### List users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users

### Create a vacation request (Alice = user 1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/vacation-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "startDate": "2026-06-01",
  "endDate": "2026-06-05",
  "reason": "Summer trip"
}

### Get Alice's requests
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vacation-requests/user/1

### Get all requests
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vacation-requests

### Filter by status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/vacation-requests?status=Pending

### Approve request #1
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/vacation-requests/1/approve

### Reject without comment (should fail with 400)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/vacation-requests/1/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Reject with comment (should succeed)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/vacation-requests/2/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comments": "Team is short-staffed that week"
}